The paper discusses a technique for image compression using Vector Quantization, which is a common topic in computer vision and multimedia (cs.MM, cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of optimization algorithms for codebook generation, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.NE).
